8 Statement of purpose of bill as introduced: This bill proposes to approve
9 amendments to the charter of the City of Rutland to limit the maximum
10 penalty for violation of an ordinance to the maximum penalties authorized
11 under 24 V.S.A. § 1974, increase the taxon the grand list for purposes of
12 replacing fire equipment, establish a taxon the grand list for purposes of
13 replacing police equipment, require the City’s Purchasing Agent to make
14 purchases based on bids whenever the value of the proposed purchase exceeds
15 the amount established in the City’s Purchasing Policy, reorganize the
16 composition of the Board of Commissioners of the Rutland Redevelopment
17 Authority, and establish staggered terms for the members of Board of
18 Commissioners of the Authority.
