2 § 17.3. REQUISITIONS
3 (a) All purchases made under section 17.1 of this charter shall be made
4 upon written requisitions therefor upon the Purchasing Agent. The Purchasing
5 Agent shall immediately proceed to purchase under the provisions of the
6 ordinances the property so required and to distribute it accordingly taking a
7 receipt therefor upon the original requisition. The Purchasing Agent shall then
8 forward the requisition to the City Clerk. Purchases in excess of $3,000.00 the
9 amount identified in the City’s Purchasing Policy shall be awarded upon bids
10 as hereinafter set forth in this subchapter.
